title: Half A Rack (w/ Shane Gillis)
description: Jay tells stories of being a young boy going bass fishing with a real man in Florida & ruining Disney World for his dad’s new family. Controversy explodes as Shane Gillis admits to sleeping naked when he and Dan Soder share a hotel room.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
